text: @MitchGayns @politi_geek @AOC Not sure how a different path means a different destination. But why now? Why do we need it now? Where was the need say 4-8 years ago? Because it sounds like a good arguing point? Just asking. We all want the same thing for our country. Just can’t agree how to get there.
